{
  "stem": "22836.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I been in the Russian army.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I skipped that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We don't talk about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Talk about the Russian army.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What did the Russian army, they take us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They take us when we come to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] after the-- after the-- everything with the partisans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then they-- then took-- then the Russians took the whole-- there was-- we was about 30-- about 30 youngsters, about 30 men, maybe.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they took us back on the front.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they took us on the front.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they took us to [NON-ENGLISH] to learn us how to shoot, how to-- how to do it when we come on the war.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then we was four weeks in [INAUDIBLE], they call this, what they teach us, four weeks.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And after that, they took us on the front.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I've been-- went through Latvia, Estonia, we went through.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were some days-- some days was the-- the-- the-- the German was so running and we couldn't run after that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some-- some days, they was running so fast back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We couldn't run.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We was-- we was saying to ourself, ah, we just stop a minute.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We don't fill the food, nothing, because you have to walk after that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Have to walk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then-- then we went on the-- then we went again on the front.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in the front was-- he send us-- he send us-- the commandeer, the head of the Otriad, the head.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He sends us to go see what's going on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were staying this side was a lake.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the other side was the German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He always keep me near him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He always keep me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "When something, you go, he take me with me him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He trust me.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
